<subSubSection id="C3136AEB5750FFB4FF085836FD982205" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB639605750FFB4FF085836FD982205" blockId="23.[151,1437,638,952]" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">
<emphasis id="B97DE5725750FFB4FF085836FEBC23D1" bold="true" box="[151,267,638,664]" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EF9844915750FFB4FE8E5836FE0C23D1" author="Galiano, M. E." box="[273,443,638,664]" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" pagination="285 - 301" refId="ref17400" refString="Galiano, M. E. (1988) Revision de los generos del grupo Hurieae (Araneae, Salticidae). Journal of Arachnology, 15, 285 - 301." type="journal article" year="1988">Galiano (1988)</bibRefCitation>
pointed out the similarity between 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E35750FFB4FCDB5836FC4E23D1" authorityName=": Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[836,1017,638,664]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadratarius">
<emphasis id="B97DE5725750FFB4FCDB5836FC4E23D1" box="[836,1017,638,664]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Si. quadratarius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E35750FFB4FBB05836FB5023D1" authorityName=": Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[1071,1255,638,664]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="campestratus">
<emphasis id="B97DE5725750FFB4FBB05836FB5023D1" box="[1071,1255,638,664]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Si. campestratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9844915750FFB4FB6A5836FA2023D1" author="Galiano, M. E." box="[1269,1431,638,664]" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" pagination="273 - 470" refId="ref17277" refString="Galiano, M. E. (1963) Las especies americanas de aranas de la familia Salticidae descriptas por Eugene Simon: Redescripciones basadas en los ejemplares tipicos. Physis, 23 (66), 273 - 470." type="journal article" year="1963">Galiano (1963</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EF9844915750FFB4FF0858EAFF6723F5" author="Galiano, M. E." box="[151,208,674,700]" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" pagination="285 - 301" refId="ref17400" refString="Galiano, M. E. (1988) Revision de los generos del grupo Hurieae (Araneae, Salticidae). Journal of Arachnology, 15, 285 - 301." type="journal article" year="1988">1988</bibRefCitation>
) highlighted that the only difference between the two species was that the cephalothorax of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E35750FFB4FB7A58EAFA2B23F5" authorityName=": Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[1253,1436,674,700]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadratarius">
<emphasis id="B97DE5725750FFB4FB7A58EAFA2B23F5" box="[1253,1436,674,700]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Si. quadratarius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was higher, and the posterior eye row was wider than in 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E35750FFB4FCAF588EFC5B23A9" authorityName=": Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[816,1004,710,736]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="campestratus">
<emphasis id="B97DE5725750FFB4FCAF588EFC5B23A9" box="[816,1004,710,736]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Si. campestratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. These differences are not enough to maintain these names as separate species. In addition, regarding distribution, it is observed that the two species have the same geographic and altitudinal distribution in 
<collectingRegion id="49CDF7825750FFB4FD525946FC952261" box="[717,802,782,808]" country="Venezuela" name="Aragua" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Aragua</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F31E79F05750FFB4FCB25946FC132261" box="[813,932,782,808]" name="Venezuela" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
. Therefore, we consider 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E35750FFB4FB295946FADC2261" authorityName=": Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[1206,1387,782,808]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadratarius">
<emphasis id="B97DE5725750FFB4FB295946FADC2261" box="[1206,1387,782,808]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Si. quadratarius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a senior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C0942E35750FFB4FEF0597AFD902205" authorityName=": Galiano" authorityYear="1988" box="[367,551,818,844]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Simonurius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="23" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="campestratus">
<emphasis id="B97DE5725750FFB4FEF0597AFD902205" box="[367,551,818,844]" italics="true" pageId="23" pageNumber="454">Si. campestratus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
